<P>
 Dodger Stadium's most famous hurler: That, of course, is celebrity vendor 
Roger (the Peanut Man) Owens, famed for his long behind-the-back tosses.  
</P>
<P>
 We were worried when we heard he was seen tossing goobers this week at a 
California League game in Adelanto (near Victorville). 
</P>
<P>
