<HEADLINE>
<P>
DON HENLEY AND CO. 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Regarding the motivation behind the Eagles' reunion (is it the money or the 
music?): After attending the concert at Irvine Meadows on June 1, I believe the 
real question is: What is the IRS going to do next year when Don Henley 
declares four new dependents on his tax return? 
</P>
<P>
 PENNY GILBERT 
</P>
<P>
 Newport Beach 
</P>
