<P>
SHOLOM ALEICHEM FEST 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I want to thank the Los Angeles Times for the excellent articles about the 
festival for Sholom Aleichem that took place at the Orange County Jewish 
Community Center on June 5 ("Around and About," OC Live!, June 2; "On the Man 
Behind 'Fiddler on the Roof,' " Calendar, June 4). 
</P>
<P>
 The stories, by Benjamin Epstein, covered all the essential details and 
captured the flavor of the festival. I most appreciated his checking with me 
several times to clarify things. Best of all, he asked me intelligent and 
penetrating questions about the event that also helped me to better understand 
it as a whole. 
</P>
<P>
 VICKI FELDON 
</P>
<P>
