<DOCID> 054781 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
June 25, 1994, Saturday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 6; Column 5; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
