<TEXT>
<P>
 Early games in the World Cup soccer championships have drawn decent TV 
ratings, but David Letterman and his writers have come up with ways to make the 
sport even more exciting. 
</P>
<P>
 Among the suggestions he offered on CBS' "Late Show With David Letterman" 
Thursday night: 
</P>
<P>
 * Let 'em use their damn hands!  
</P>
<P>
