<TEXT>
<P>
 Soccer Team -- A story Friday about the U.S. soccer team's stay at a Dana 
Point hotel inaccurately described how former Dallas Cowboys coach Jimmy 
Johnson arrived at a convention for sports editors. He came by limousine. A 
helicopter and police escort were for another party. 
</P>
